data.description: Welcome to this charming three-bedroom, two-bathroom home located in the heart of Chickasha. With its traditional style and thoughtfully designed features, this residence offers a comfortable and inviting living space for you and your family. The living room boasts a cozy fireplace with a beautiful brick design, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for gatherings and relaxation. The kitchen, with its cute traditional cabinets, offers ample storage and counter space, making meal preparation a breeze. The formal dining area provides an elegant space for hosting dinner parties or enjoying family meals. Each bedroom is spacious and versatile to your needs. There's a built-in laundry room right off the kitchen. The front yard is equipped with an invisible dog fence, allowing your furry friends to roam freely and safely. For added security, the property features a reliable security system, offering peace of mind for you and your loved ones.  Don't miss your chance to own this lovely three-bedroom, two-bathroom home in Chickasha. With its traditional charm, convenient features, and attractive financing options, this property offers an exceptional opportunity for comfortable and secure living. Schedule a showing today and envision yourself enjoying the comforts of this delightful residence.
